article.description: Te'Jon Lucas had a career-high 26 points as Milwaukee edged Morgan State 62-57 in the Islands of the Bahamas Showcase on Saturday.
article.headline: Lucas scores 26 to lead Milwaukee over Morgan St. 62-57
article.linkText: Lucas scores 26 to lead Milwaukee over Morgan St. 62-57
article.story: NASSAU, Bahamas -- Te'Jon Lucas had a career-high 26 points as Milwaukee edged Morgan State 62-57 in the Islands of the Bahamas Showcase on Saturday. DeAndre Abram had 14 points for Milwaukee (5-2). Darius Roy added seven assists. Sherwyn Devonish-Prince Jr. had 13 points for the Bears (3-4). Isaiah Burke added 12 points. Stanley Davis had 12 points and nine rebounds. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
